snippet.title: Mimic Hunter AdvJam2017 Trailer
snippet.description:
Release trailer for our GameJolt Adventure Jam 2017 #AdvJam2017 game "Mimic Hunter" that was made in 2 weeks from scratch. Was hell of a ride--and it's not over! The game may very possibly be developed further for a more complete version in the future!

You can download the AdvJam version for free here: http://gamejolt.com/games/mimic_hunter/255368, and vote for it here: http://jams.gamejolt.io/advjam2017/games/mimic_hunter/255368!

Remember to check out all the other cool little games made for the Jam! http://jams.gamejolt.io/advjam2017/games
